  "text": "Validated human APC sgRNA [CITATION_1] and sgControl primers were subcloned into Lenti-CRISPR-V2 64 (Addgene plasmid #52961). H82 cells were infected with Lenti-V2-sgAPC or sgControl lentivirus and stable polyclonal pools were selected with puromycin.",
